1
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,240
Mr. Zhen.

2
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:45,360
Hao Feng.

3
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,520
I've told you many times.

4
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:48,920
Between us,

5
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,440
