8
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:54,840
Okay, Brother Era.

9
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,280
The funds of Memory Tree Public Fund

10
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:58,120
have never been invested in the laboratory.

11
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:58,800
And

12
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,440
about the live clinical trial you mentioned,

13
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,840
I don't think it's the right time.

14
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,280
There's been a lot of negative public opinion recently.

15
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,560
I'm still looking into it.

16
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:08,080
Don't rush.

17
00:01:08,080 --> 00:01:09,840
Let's get things straight before we talk about it.

18
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,680
You suggested before

19
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,320
