20
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,480
I don't understand finance.

21
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:18,680
It's all on your side to implement.

22
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,640
But if we can't provide effective feedback

23
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,080
to the public for the time being,

24
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,800
can we cancel it?

25
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,040
Dr. Hao,

26
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,880
leave these formalities

27
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,280
to me.

28
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,400
You need to be patient

29
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,200
