31
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,560
That's it for now.

32
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,440
I have something to deal with.

33
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:37,720
I...

34
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:41,560
Hello?

35
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,560
Hello?

36
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,760
Are you from Zhen Era?

37
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:40,160
I saw you together with my own eyes.

38
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:44,960
Three years ago,

39
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,440
you became my personal assistant.

40
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,400
We met Zhen Shida many times.

41
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,400
You always acted like you didn't know each other.

42
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,440
But why

43
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,880
