44
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,360
Are you hiding something from me?

45
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,000
I'm fully devoted to my experiments.

46
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,280
You are the only one

47
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,400
