48
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,000
I hope you tell me the truth.

49
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,040
He wants to kill you.

50
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,480
You should go.

51
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,800
I'm not your enemy.

52
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,880
You can call me H.

53
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,640
I've been tracking a

54
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:38,360
