55
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,160
Their code name is J.

56
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,120
During an accidental operation,

57
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,240
I intervened

58
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,120
