65
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,880
But the clues I have suggest

66
00:04:57,880 --> 00:05:00,520
he's more dangerous than you think.

67
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,680
This accident wasn't an accident.

68
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,520
The violent impact

69
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,280
caused severe concussion,

70
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:07,160
resulting in retrograde amnesia.

71
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,800
So when he woke up,

72
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,960
he had memory gaps.

73
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,400
If he gradually recovers in the future,

74
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,240
and remembers something,

75
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,160
he can use the email address at the end of the letter

76
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,080
to contact me.

77
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,160
Remember,

78
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,400
