82
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,720
You...

83
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,000
You should just forget it.

84
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,680
Let him talk.

85
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,720
Ten years ago,

86
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,600
Zhen Shida,

87
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:02,160
