94
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,120
and became a philanthropist.

95
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,520
His persona as a philanthropist

96
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:20,320
greatly enhanced his business halo,

97
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,040
causing his venture capital projects

98
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,080
to always have backers.

99
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,200
Moreover,

100
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:27,080
all the donations he gave to those welfare homes

101
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,000
were fraudulent.

102
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,360
Secondly,

103
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,560
according to reliable information,

104
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,640
he has now turned the Cixin Welfare Home

105
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,880
into a money laundering tool

106
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,360
for those unscrupulous tycoons.

107
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,680
His paintings,

108
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,680
his watches,

109
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,400
his assets,

110
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,560
his money,

111
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,120
