112
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,920
It's all dirty money he's made.

113
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,160
Such a person

114
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,880
is simply rotten to the core.

115
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,560
And over the years,

116
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,960
he has even engaged in the trafficking

117
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:57,080
of children from the orphanage.

118
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,440
My idol,

119
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,280
you continue.

120
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,520
We want him

121
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,920
invest all the money

122
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,120
from the Zhen Era Foundation

123
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,320
in charity

124
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,560
for real.

125
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,160
Then we'll expose the orphanage

126
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,960
and ruin his image

127
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,160
as a good person.

128
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,960
That way,

129
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,480
the orphanage

130
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,080
will get real help.

131
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,000
That's not all.

132
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,160
I want him

133
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,000
and the scam of Memory Tree.

134
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,320
I want him

135
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,800
to tell the truth.

136
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,160
From now on,

137
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,600
you are

138
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,240
Wu Ke.

139
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:33,720
Impressive.

140
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,400
Now,

141
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,400
the game continues.

142
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,400
Wu...

143
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,160
Wu Ke.

144
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:58,920
Remember,

145
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,200
report to me immediately

146
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,080
if anyone enters or leaves without permission,

147
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,120
or if there are any suspicious individuals.

148
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,920
Understood.

149
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,320
Take it slow, you two.

150
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,320
Be careful not to fall.

151
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,000
This is our dormitory.

152
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,040
Just take a quick look.

153
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,440
Okay.

154
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,240
This is our activity room.

155
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,600
The children usually have

156
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,880
art and music classes here.

157
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,520
Hello, High Court.

158
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,680
Okay, I'll be right there.

159
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,280
Wait for me here.

160
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:28,800
Don't wander around.

161
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,440
The actual situation here is not good.

162
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,280
It's just window dressing.

163
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,960
Mo Wen is rather cautious.

164
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,200
Get in touch with her more.

165
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,400
It's enough to leave an impression on her.

166
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,360
Got it.

167
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,480
But we have to

168
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,160
change the situation of these children quickly.

169
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,640
Stop.

170
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,520
What's on that windowsill?

171
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,120
Roses.

172
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,280
Wu Ke.

173
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,120
Mr. Mo.

174
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:26,560
What are you doing?

175
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,800
I just came here.

176
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:29,680
I'm taking a look around.

177
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,480
To get familiar with the place.

178
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,760
You just came here.

179
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,640
You don't know this place well.

180
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,720
Don't wander around.

181
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,720
and scare the children.

182
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,200
I see.

183
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,040
Mr. Mo,

184
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,880
