185
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,880
This is the punishment room of the orphanage.

186
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,560
Those who make mistakes

187
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,960
and refuse to correct them

188
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,360
will be locked up here

189
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,360
to reflect on their mistakes.

190
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,480
I see.

191
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,080
I thought

192
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,240
