193
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,480
You just came here.

194
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,760
I can forgive you this time.

195
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,080
Don't say that again.

196
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,760
I'm sorry.

197
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:06,560
The windowsill is dusty.

198
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,560
It means the children are well-behaved.

199
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,240
Right?

200
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,600
Yes.

201
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,520
Since the child left,

202
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,080
