203
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,560
has never been opened.

204
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,040
The child?

205
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,600
There was a child before.

206
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,440
He was quiet,

207
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,280
and had a solitary personality.

208
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,880
Later on, it was found out

209
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:26,320
that he had autism.

210
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,200
He was sent to the hospital for several months.

211
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,040
Unexpectedly, after he came back,

212
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,040
his personality changed dramatically.

213
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,640
We had no choice

214
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,200
but to put him

215
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,520
in this punishment room.

216
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,960
That child

217
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,240
poor boy.

218
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,120
He was a good boy,

219
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,480
and he was very talented.

220
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,440
He liked painting.

221
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,520
As long as he picked up a paintbrush

222
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,120
in this classroom,

223
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,680
he would be quiet.

224
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,920
But it's a pity that

225
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,760
he died because of

226
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,280
complications.

227
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,120
When did this happen?

228
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:10,080
It's been over a year.

229
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,160
Alright, that's enough.

230
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:14,360
You go ahead.

231
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,800
Wu Ke.

232
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:30,320
Mr. Mo.

233
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,080
Good,

234
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,120
