237
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:34,760
Alright.

238
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,080
Mr. Mo,

239
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,440
this is...

240
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,080
The foundation

241
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,560
