247
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,200
I'm just tidying up for them.

248
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:01,040
Student aid is a good thing.

249
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:01,520
Let me do it.

250
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:02,560
Yes.

251
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,440
Ten years ago,

252
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,800
Zhen Era Charity Foundation

253
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:08,560
took over our orphanage,

254
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:10,160
and that's how the Student Aid Program started.

255
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:12,160
After that, Dean Gao took over the management.

256
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,360
Those children who were sent away

257
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,880
should be grateful to the orphanage, right?

258
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:18,880
Are there still any contacts?

259
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,720
I still remember

260
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,120
a child named Huai Yuan,

261
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,920
who was particularly close to me.

262
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:34,080
But since he left,

263
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,960
not a single letter,

264
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,360
not a single phone call has come back.

265
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:45,760
It's the past.

266
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,680
Don't mention it.

267
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:47,480
This should be moved out.

268
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,040
OK.

269
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,320
Wu Ke

270
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,120
It's okay.

271
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,160
I tripped.

272
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:13,600
Be careful.

273
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,360
You scared me.
